&lt;li&gt;You have experience managing the holistic life cycle of a client relationship from onboarding, quarterly business reviews, renewal, and upsells&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have experience selling into large enterprises, negotiating contracts with sophisticated procurement teams, and liaising with senior executives across several business functions such as strategy, sales, marketing, and data/insights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have experience managing a book of business and or selling a new complex product or service.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have a track record of not only meeting but &lt;strong&gt;exceeding sales goals&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/l

